### Basket Service - Get User Basket
GET {{baseAddress}}/v1/baskets/user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Basket Service - Add Item to Basket
POST {{baseAddress}}/v1/baskets/item
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "courseId":"{{courseId}}",
  "courseName": "Python",
  "coursePrice": 200
}


### Order Service - Create Order
POST {{baseAddress}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
{
  "Address": {
    "Line": "123 Main St",
    "Province": "Ontario",
    "District": "Toronto",
    "ZipCode": "12345",
    "Street": "Main St"
  },
  "Payment": {
    "CardNumber": "4111111111111111",
    "CardHolderName": "John Doe",
    "Expiration": "12/25",
    "Cvc": "123",
    "Amount": 150.75
  },
  "Items": [
    {
      "ProductId": "{{courseId}}",
      "ProductName": "Python",
      "UnitPrice": 200
    }
  ]
}

### Create a Payment
POST {{baseAddress}}/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json,
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
{
  "OrderCode": "6657c883-2e9b-43e4-a421-45f9ef25b415",
  "CardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "CardHolderName": "John Doe",
  "CardExpirationDate": "12/25",
  "CardSecurityNumber": "123",
  "Amount": 150.75
}

### Get All Payments
GET {{baseAddress}}/v1/payments
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###